29 void TwizyController::start() {
30  new Motors(*supervisor_, nh_);
31  new Realsense(*supervisor_, nh_, "front");
32  new Realsense(*supervisor_, nh_, "rear");
33  new Piksi(*supervisor_, nh_, nh_private_, "left");
34  new Piksi(*supervisor_, nh_, nh_private_, "right");
35  new WheelEncoder(*supervisor_, nh_, nh_private_, "left");
36  new WheelEncoder(*supervisor_, nh_, nh_private_, "right");
37  new Velodyne(*supervisor_, nh_);
38 
39  webots::Node *robot = supervisor_->getSelf();
40 
41  geometry_msgs::PointStamped position;
42  position.header.frame_id = "map";
43  while (supervisor_->step(supervisor_->getBasicTimeStep()) != -1 &&
44  ros::ok()) {
45  ros::spinOnce();
46 
47  if (use_sim_time_) {
48  rosgraph_msgs::Clock clock;
49  double time = supervisor_->getTime();
50  clock.clock.sec = (int)time;
51  // round prevents precision issues that can cause problems with ROS
52  // timers
53  clock.clock.nsec = round(1000 * (time - clock.clock.sec)) * 1.0e+6;
54  clock_publisher_.publish(clock);
55  }
56 
57  const double *wb_position = robot->getPosition();
58  position.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
59  position.point.x = wb_position[2];
60  position.point.y = wb_position[0];
61  position.point.z = wb_position[1];
62 
63  position_publisher_.publish(position);
64  }
65 }
